items.title: Introsort - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
Introsort or introspective sort is a hybrid sorting algorithm that provides both fast 
average performance and (asymptotically) optimal worst-case performance.
items.htmlSnippet:
Introsort or introspective sort is a hybrid sorting algorithm that provides both fast

items.title: Introselect - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
Introsort achieves practical performance comparable to quicksort while 
preserving O(n log n) worst-case behavior by creating a hybrid of quicksort and 
heapsort.
